readTermPolicy: Please read our privacy policy to understand our online information practices and the choices you can make as a user about the way your information is collected and used. You may also find this policy published on our homepage.
TermPolicy_2: This policy is applicable to all information stored or collected on our website. On some pages, you can order products, make requests, and register to receive information. The types of personal information collected at these pages are:
TermPolicy_permission_1: - We are using CAMERA and STORAGE permissions to capture user's images and pick images from device gallery for better user experience.
TermPolicy_permission_2: - We are using the phone number that user registers, for the purpose of user verification via one-time password (security code). (One-time password will be sent by Twillio).
TermPolicy_permission_3: - We are collecting user's location stored in the system for locating our nearest agent for service purpose.
TermPolicy_info: HOW YOUR INFORMATION IS USED BY US
TermPolicy_info_1: As a user, when you register or place any enquiry, you are requested to provide us personal information. We use your given information for that particular enquiry only. We do not pass on this information to third parties except to the extent necessary to complete that particular order.
TermPolicy_3: We use return email addresses to answer the email we receive. Such addresses are not used for any other purpose and are not shared with outside parties.
TermPolicy_4: We may only use your email address to send you the relevant marketing information about AICP MOTOR App.that might interest you. You can opt-out of receiving future marketing materials at any time. You can unsubscribe by following the instructions contained in the messages you receive. You can also change your preferences for marketing in your user profile. Even if you opt-out of receiving these messages, we reserve the right to send you certain communications necessary to the services we provide. We may also send you service announcements and administrative messages. We strongly not recommend to opt-out of receiving those communications as they are important for a user to know.
TermPolicy_5: Finally, we never use or share the personally identifiable information provided to us online in ways unrelated to the ones described above, we also providing you an opportunity to opt out or otherwise prohibit such unrelated uses.
TermPolicy_Security_1: To maintain data accuracy, we have put in place the appropriate physical, electronic, and managerial procedures to safeguard and secure the information we collect online.
TermPolicy_Enforcement_1: We make every effort to comply with law enforcement and investigative agencies to prevent crime and/or the sale of stolen devices on our website.  AICP MOTOR. has right to inspect or disclose to any appropriate third party any information provided by you to AICP MOTOR. to assist in the prevention, investigation, and prosecution of crime.
TermPolicy_Information_1: You can access all your personally identifiable information that we collect online and securely store by emailing to aicpmpn.fb.pkg@gmail.com. To protect your privacy and security, we will take reasonable steps to verify your identity before granting access or making your personal data adjustment.
TermPolicy_Contract_1: If you have any futher questions or any concern regards our privacy policy, please email us at aicppkg@gmail.com
